; Coverage test for amount.cc lines 1043-1058
; Exercise the period-followed-by-digit path in amount parsing
; When an amount ends with a period followed by a digit in an expression,
; the period is put back (line 1058)

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food            $10.00
    Assets:Cash

; Use format with expression that puts a period then digit context
; The "1." should be parsed as "1" with trailing period stripped
test eval "1+2"
3
end test

; Exercise amount with trailing period in expression context
test eval "10 + 5"
15
end test
